title: Missouri S&T’s EWB to host 5K on Halloween (Missouri University of Science & Technology)
text: ( Source : Missouri University of Science & Technology ) The student chapter of Engineers Without Borders ( EWB ) at Missouri University of Science and Technology will host a 5K run this month to raise money to support team travel expenses.
